      "id": "7e68b7846a5e9525",
      "text": "Finally, Understanding is “Model Free” and Reasoning is “Model Based”. This is likely the most important distinction to people who are implementing intelligent systems since it provides a way to keep the implementation on the correct path when the going gets rough. We cannot discuss these issues quite yet, but if you are curious you can watch the videos at vimeo.com which discuss this distinction at length. Think of their appearance in this table as a kind of foreshadowing."
